    <note>Zhang(1) Chan [174] Shuchun's [288] father, Lu(1) Min's [7050] father-in-law, Wu(3) Jin's [7394] grandfather-in-law. Another son, Zhongzi [3133], was Hunnan tiju in 1177. According to Zhu(1) Xi [3257], when Qin(1) Gui [8008] strongly advocated a policy of peaceful coexistence with Jin, only Hu(1) Quan [10565] and Zhang(1) Chan, among the shi dafu, maintained from first to last that there was no way that peace could be concluded with Jin. Zhou Bida, WJ, 61.2b; XNYL, 177.14b, 183.8a, 13a; Lou Yue, WJ, 104.21a. CBD, 3, 2333-4.</note>
